			<storyAction>0,3,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>5,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:主公，东吴的命运还有希望！请您不要泄气！</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,2,76</storyAction>
			<dialogue>76,孙权:……周瑜。有件事我想问你。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:不知主公所问何事？</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>76,孙权:逼死刘备的既然是我们东吴，那么对蜀国来说，我们就是仇敌。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>76,孙权:但是赤壁之战中，蜀军却为我吴国作战，这究竟是怎么回事？</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:主公，公瑾的内心也问着自己，那么公瑾就全盘托出吧。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,1,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>5,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:其实周瑜皓洁之心已经受污，与不义之徒立下誓约了。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>76,孙权:孔明是吗……果然如此。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,3,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>8,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:孔明是个悖主忘义之徒，他为了掌握蜀国的实权，打算谋害主公的性命。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>76,孙权:孔明谋害刘备……？孔明竟然……我真不敢相信！</dialogue>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:孔明挥舞着污秽的双翼，翩然来到公瑾镇守的家园，泛起蛊惑的笑容提出了交易。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,1,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>5,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:他说只要我们帮他杀死刘备，就把荆州割让给我们！</dialogue>
			<dialogue>76,孙权:嗯。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:……公瑾便与他立下这个誓约。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,3,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>8,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:后来公瑾助他成功地消灭了刘备。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:也换得了富饶的荆州做为回报。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,1,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:可是，我周瑜万万也没有想到，奸贼曹操竟会侵吴……</dialogue>
			<storyAction>19,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:公瑾所做一切只是为了东吴，为了东吴能够统一天下……</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,3,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>13,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:还请主公恕罪。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>76,孙权:……嗯，你这么做也是无可奈何的。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>76,孙权:不过，如今到了这个地步，我们该如何是好？</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:位于前线的濡须口，是守护都城建业的门户重地，我军必须于此地阻止曹军的攻势。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,77</storyAction>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:主公，为保家园免受曹贼的践踏，我将集结各地剩余的兵力前往濡须口。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:主公能否在周瑜赶回之前，加强濡须口的防御？</dialogue>
			<dialogue>76,孙权:嗯，好吧。我会命令陆逊重整水军的。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>77,周瑜:那么周瑜暂且告别主公。</dialogue>
			<dialogue>76,孙权:嗯，有劳你了。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,77</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
