			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>8,4,20</storyAction>
			<dialogue>20,荀彧:是的，这的确是一场漂亮的胜仗。即使是强大的东吴水军，恐怕一时也难以恢复元气了。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,20</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,2,23</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>8,4,23</storyAction>
			<dialogue>23,贾诩:主公，不可错过这个大好良机，一鼓作气消灭东吴吧。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,23</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:嗯。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,2,19</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>8,4,19</storyAction>
			<dialogue>19,司马懿:不过主公，仲达于赤壁吴营中发现一座红色祭坛，着实令人起疑。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,19</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:嗯。司马懿，你认为它有何用途？</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,19</storyAction>
			<dialogue>19,司马懿:属下也无法知悉。或许是祈祷之用吧……</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,19</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>5,4,1</storyAction>
			<dialogue>1,夏侯惇:喂喂，那玩意儿该不会是危急时，请求神明保佑的东西吧？</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,1</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,0,19</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>8,4,19</storyAction>
			<dialogue>19,司马懿:不，将军此言差矣。诚如周瑜之辈，焉有借助神力之理。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,19</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:嗯，如今争论不休也无济于事。此时应该全心对付吴军才是。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,2,19</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>8,4,19</storyAction>
			<dialogue>19,司马懿:是。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,19</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:文若，吴军现在何处？</dialogue>
			<storyAction>8,4,20</storyAction>
			<dialogue>20,荀彧:已经撤退至建业附近的濡须口。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,20</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,1,0</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:濡须口……在建业的附近是吧？那么吴军必然会奋力死战。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,2,1</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>5,4,1</storyAction>
			<dialogue>1,夏侯惇:不过孟德，我们也不能因此驻足不前啊。</dialogue>
			<storyAction>0,4,1</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>0,3,0</storyAction>
			<dealyTime>0.3</dealyTime>
			<storyAction>19,4,0</storyAction>
			<dialogue>0,曹操:嗯。好吧，前往濡须口！我们要彻底打垮吴军！</dialogue>
